Title: Paul Smith Extreme EDT  -  100 ml(For Men)
Description: Few things can be as refreshing as starting the day with a fresh, spicy fragrance. Bask in this mild, citrusy aroma from Paul Smith, designed for men who love their perfumes subtle. Launched in 2003, the Paul Smith Extreme Man is a luxury fragrance from perfumers Marie-Aude Couture-Bluche and Olivier Pescheux. With dominant fresh spicy and woody accords, this Eau de Toilette brings a crisp combination of citrus and spices that remind you of a sprightly spring day, sprinkled with the brightness of summer. The top notes of this Paul Smith Extreme Man perfume are Bergamot and lemon, both being instantly noticeable with the first spray. As it settles down, the heart notes emerge with Rosemary, Nutmeg and Geranium. The Base notes for this Paul Smith fragrance are Tonka bean and brazilian rosewood, that linger on with impressive longevity and sillage. This Woody Aromatic fragrance comes exquisitely packaged in a clear glass bottle with an urbane, contemporary square design. The seductive charm of this sensuous, ultra-masculine scent is delightfully unforgettable and perfect for a natural, daily wear.

Title: J. Del Pozo Halloween Kiss Sexy EDC  -  100 ml(For Women)
Description: Fruity and floral, Halloween Kiss Sexy from the Spanish fashion house of Jesus Del Pozo is the definition of sensual femininity. Sweet and sensual, Halloween Kiss Sexy was created by perfumer Christophe Raynaud as an emblem for the cosmopolitan woman who is unafraid to express herself without taking recourse to false modesty. Like pink flowers wrapped in velvety, creamy caramel, this luxurious Eau de Toilette lifts your spirits and enshrouds you in a cloud of flowery, refreshing essences reminiscent of a spring-time romance. Invigorating like a passionate first embrace, the refreshing top note of Halloween Kiss Sexy opens with green apple, lemon and peach juice. The floral heart of peony, freesia and cyclamen add a refreshing sweetness to the fragrance and trail into a warm, heady base note of sandalwood and velvety musk. Like the yin to Halloween's yang, Halloween Kiss Sexy is for a woman who takes charge. Not for her the role of a victim, she is the perpetrator, fearless and uninhibited.
